episodes.title: Raised In A Cult
episodes.description: Growing up in the Mormon religion, Payton faced unimaginable abuse within her own family. However, she found the strength to break her silence and simultaneously make the difficult decision to leave the Mormon church. Join us as we explore Payton's inspiring story of resilience, shedding light on the importance of speaking up and finding one's own path to healing.
subjects: The Church Of Jesus Christ Of Latter-Day Saints
